      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but i've read a lot online that st johns wort is just a natural herb so it shouldn't be that bad to mix with regular stuff. my doctor is actually super busy and i can't really get an appointment before my exams start next week. do you know how much of a risk it actually is? like, is it really something i should worry about or is it just a minor thing?",
