      "content": "i hear you, but i already bought the supplement and it's like 30 euros so i really don't want to waste it. if i just take a very small amount, like maybe half the recommended dose, wouldn't that make it safe enough? i'm not trying to do anything crazy, just looking for a little extra support so i can actually focus on my studies. surely a small dose wouldn't trigger anything major?",
